      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs super smooth, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
