    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-performing car that has been treated with care. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, though you will find a few minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the hood and small scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats remain supple with only light creasing on the driver's bolster. All technological features\u2014including the infotainment system, climate control, and power windows\u2014are in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is in its prime. It has a documented service history, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of brake pads installed last month. The engine runs quietly, and the transmission delivers smooth, confident shifts. This car is turn-key ready and offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
